{"tid":1380211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月30號要罷工好難，因為仲有巴士番工！","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:01:09.000Z","uid":117622,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"90d3239a62224cb5573f25c26a12a9ed785e9361","tid":1380211,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"地鐵搞得店都仲有巴士，為左個日要準時返工，一定要早幾個鐘落街搭車！<br />\n<br />\n就算你個日幾點返工，返工地點有幾遠，都要早過頭班車落街，因為有機會係主要幹道都會大塞車。<br />\n<br />\n發動全港所有地點搭頭班車返工，以高舉長遮為記認，可以及時阻止到有人搞事，令到全香港都搭唔到頭班車返工。<br />\n<br />\n你知啦，搭唔到頭班車返工，就大條道理同老世講返唔到工，就會大罷工！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"0325c77ab2f9adcf774afe05b3f5f0ad45a72c0d","tid":1380211,"uid":172257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9hpVk4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9hpVk4.png&h=ac8c36ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf8bcc7f272699d5e537ab9f732dbfc7c528458e","tid":1380211,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"太散，罷工分好多日，文宣亦做唔夠"},{"pid":"e3a6ae7bc3033c5340ff616d0339ea49bacfe240","tid":1380211,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"公司有免費穿梭巴士接送<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ee63435618cd8b876080ccde611473132dd4e7","tid":1380211,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會喇 你望下之前狗鐵死車之後的返工情況 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"59974cbe18deee5ad40fb224752cbcecce588706","tid":1380211,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3a6ae7bc3033c5340ff616d0339ea49bacfe240","tid":1380211,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"公司有免費穿梭巴士接送<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"封咗路，有巴士有咩用？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住早幾個鐘落去搭穿梭巴士啦"},{"pid":"9fa8e87c22a46db8b1ce4b8b30410834c90813db","tid":1380211,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"39446e0295c2bbe7341bb0c0042b6634301586b6","tid":1380211,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"地鐵都未firm 無消息就805 啦"},{"pid":"0e38dc019200dcbd5d4fb66b755a14043c972e5a","tid":1380211,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:24:38.000Z","msg":"mtr 由頭到尾都冇話過會罷工，問過幾個車長fd 都話唔會！"},{"pid":"12be5dcd6b772a828ee12a573e6fbc4d0f1628a0","tid":1380211,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"玩SIM CITY，諗到個方法癱瘓交通，用封鎖帶！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba46073fa9de5465a2492777c2556d8c75c3d1e8","tid":1380211,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"如果到時全港都發生交通意外就冇得返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d1275f559fdc02e5adbcd541e23dc1ab455272","tid":1380211,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"大家都坐巴士會好塞車<br />\n等好耐都未有巴士"},{"pid":"3ebdac6f4d02ae1b67679cb1af74720444c1b4aa","tid"